    <title>Git常用命令总结</title>
    <link href="/2025/08/06/Git%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/"/>
    <url>/2025/08/06/Git%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Git-常用命令总结"><a href="#Git-常用命令总结" class="headerlink" title="Git 常用命令总结"></a>Git 常用命令总结</h1><p>Git 是目前最流行的分布式版本控制系统，掌握 Git 的基本操作对于开发者来说至关重要。本文将介绍 Git 的常用命令，帮助你快速上手 Git。</p><h2 id="基本配置"><a href="#基本配置" class="headerlink" title="基本配置"></a>基本配置</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 设置用户名</span><br>git config --global user.name <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Your Name&quot;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 设置邮箱</span><br>git config --global user.email <span class="hljs-string">&quot;your.email@example.com&quot;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 查看配置</span><br>git config --list<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="创建仓库"><a href="#创建仓库" class="headerlink" title="创建仓库"></a>创建仓库</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 初始化本地仓库</span><br>git init<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 克隆远程仓库</span><br>git <span class="hljs-built_in">clone</span> &lt;repository_url&gt;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 克隆指定分支</span><br>git <span class="hljs-built_in">clone</span> -b &lt;branch_name&gt; &lt;repository_url&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="基本操作"><a href="#基本操作" class="headerlink" title="基本操作"></a>基本操作</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 查看当前状态</span><br>git status<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 添加文件到暂存区</span><br>git add &lt;file_name&gt;<br>git add .  <span class="hljs-comment"># 添加所有更改</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 提交更改</span><br>git commit -m <span class="hljs-string">&quot;commit message&quot;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 查看提交历史</span><br>git <span class="hljs-built_in">log</span><br>git <span class="hljs-built_in">log</span> --oneline  <span class="hljs-comment"># 简洁显示</span><br>git <span class="hljs-built_in">log</span> --graph  <span class="hljs-comment"># 图形化显示分支</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="分支管理"><a href="#分支管理" class="headerlink" title="分支管理"></a>分支管理</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 查看分支</span><br>git branch<br>git branch -v  <span class="hljs-comment"># 查看分支详情</span><br>git branch -a  <span class="hljs-comment"># 查看所有分支（包括远程）</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 创建分支</span><br>git branch &lt;branch_name&gt;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 切换分支</span><br>git checkout &lt;branch_name&gt;<br>git switch &lt;branch_name&gt;  <span class="hljs-comment"># Git 2.23+ 推荐方式</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 创建并切换分支</span><br>git checkout -b &lt;branch_name&gt;<br>git switch -c &lt;branch_name&gt;  <span class="hljs-comment"># Git 2.23+ 推荐方式</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 删除分支</span><br>git branch -d &lt;branch_name&gt;  <span class="hljs-comment"># 安全删除</span><br>git branch -D &lt;branch_name&gt;  <span class="hljs-comment"># 强制删除</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 合并分支</span><br>git merge &lt;branch_name&gt;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 变基操作</span><br>git rebase &lt;branch_name&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="远程操作"><a href="#远程操作" class="headerlink" title="远程操作"></a>远程操作</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 查看远程仓库</span><br>git remote -v<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 添加远程仓库</span><br>git remote add &lt;remote_name&gt; &lt;repository_url&gt;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 从远程获取更新</span><br>git fetch &lt;remote_name&gt;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 拉取远程分支并合并</span><br>git pull &lt;remote_name&gt; &lt;branch_name&gt;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 推送本地分支到远程</span><br>git push &lt;remote_name&gt; &lt;branch_name&gt;<br>git push -u &lt;remote_name&gt; &lt;branch_name&gt;  <span class="hljs-comment"># 设置上游分支</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 删除远程分支</span><br>git push &lt;remote_name&gt; --delete &lt;branch_name&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="撤销操作"><a href="#撤销操作" class="headerlink" title="撤销操作"></a>撤销操作</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 撤销工作区修改</span><br>git checkout -- &lt;file_name&gt;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 撤销暂存区修改（取消add）</span><br>git reset HEAD &lt;file_name&gt;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 修改最后一次提交</span><br>git commit --amend<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 回退到指定提交</span><br>git reset --hard &lt;commit_id&gt;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 撤销某次提交</span><br>git revert &lt;commit_id&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="标签管理"><a href="#标签管理" class="headerlink" title="标签管理"></a>标签管理</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 查看标签</span><br>git tag<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 创建标签</span><br>git tag &lt;tag_name&gt;<br>git tag -a &lt;tag_name&gt; -m <span class="hljs-string">&quot;tag message&quot;</span>  <span class="hljs-comment"># 带注释的标签</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 推送标签到远程</span><br>git push &lt;remote_name&gt; &lt;tag_name&gt;<br>git push &lt;remote_name&gt; --tags  <span class="hljs-comment"># 推送所有标签</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 删除标签</span><br>git tag -d &lt;tag_name&gt;<br>git push &lt;remote_name&gt; :refs/tags/&lt;tag_name&gt;  <span class="hljs-comment"># 删除远程标签</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="其他实用命令"><a href="#其他实用命令" class="headerlink" title="其他实用命令"></a>其他实用命令</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 查看文件差异</span><br>git diff<br>git diff &lt;file_name&gt;<br>git diff &lt;commit_id1&gt; &lt;commit_id2&gt;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 储藏当前工作</span><br>git stash<br>git stash list  <span class="hljs-comment"># 查看储藏列表</span><br>git stash apply  <span class="hljs-comment"># 恢复最近储藏</span><br>git stash drop  <span class="hljs-comment"># 删除最近储藏</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 查看某行代码的修改历史</span><br>git blame &lt;file_name&gt;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 忽略文件（.gitignore）</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 在项目根目录创建.gitignore文件</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>这些 Git 命令涵盖了日常开发中的大部分需求。随着使用经验的增加，你会逐渐掌握更多高级用法。记住，Git 是一个强大的工具，熟练使用它将大大提高你的开发效率。</p><p>建议初学者多实践这些命令，遇到问题时可以使用 <code>git help &lt;command&gt;</code> 查看详细帮助文档。</p>]]></content>
    
    
